365
00:19:05,688 --> 00:19:07,900
Spending 58 yuan to have a meal
with someone you like

366
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,260
is already a good deal in Shanghai.

367
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:12,980
Ms. Zhao, sorry,

368
00:19:12,980 --> 00:19:13,820
