369
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:17,020
These are the written materials
for each project

370
00:19:17,266 --> 00:19:19,177
in today's proposal meeting.
Please have a look.

371
00:19:19,244 --> 00:19:20,590
I've placed your copy on your desk.

372
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,180
Speak up, Ms. Lin and I don't bite.

373
00:19:22,711 --> 00:19:23,860
I'll present the project first.

374
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:24,860
Get the projector ready.

375
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:26,700
Okay, I'll go ahead.

376
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:27,740
Thanks.

377
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,880
(I am the wife of Li Weifeng
from the South China Client Division.)

378
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,480
(Zhou Mei from the South China Client
Division is seducing a married man.)

379
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,190
(Zhou Mei from Celian Tianxia
has destroyed another family.)

380
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,460
(A notice to all staff of your company.)

381
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:00,980
Being likable is an advantage,

382
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,260
but sometimes,

383
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:03,620
it's also a disadvantage.

384
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:05,940
Everything has two sides.

385
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:08,100
When I hired you,

386
00:20:08,100 --> 00:20:09,540
I told you what our bottom line was.

387
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,555
Don't get involved with people at work.

388
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:13,500
You've crossed my bottom line.

389
00:20:14,340 --> 00:20:15,060
You work in PR.

390
00:20:15,244 --> 00:20:17,060
How do you plan to handle
your own crisis PR?

391
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:19,511
Come on, use yourself as an example.

392
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:20,820
Tell me your plan.

393
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:22,044
I don't have a plan.

394
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:24,466
This doesn't count as a crisis.

395
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:25,780
Prove it to me.

396
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,060
Fine.

397
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:29,340
Then, I need to take two hours off.

398
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:47,420
You're Zhou Mei?

399
00:20:48,060 --> 00:20:48,580
Yes.

400
00:20:48,977 --> 00:20:50,400
What are you doing here?

401
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:51,460
Looking for you.

402
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,060
Do you know who I am?

403
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:55,500
Li Weifeng's wife.

404
00:20:56,100 --> 00:20:56,860
We haven't met.

405
00:20:59,260 --> 00:21:01,020
But not only do you know
what I look like,

406
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:04,660
but you also sent a letter
to my company to report me.

407
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:09,460
How did you know I was here?

408
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:10,740
Li Weifeng told me.

409
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:13,660
Not only did he tell me

410
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:15,780
that you go to the yoga studio
every Monday morning,

411
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:17,660
but he also told me that at 6 PM,

412
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:20,333
you go to Giraffe English School
to take your child to English class.

413
00:21:21,288 --> 00:21:23,688
The reason I didn't go
to Giraffe English School to find you

414
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:26,111
is that I didn't want to
embarrass you in front of your child.

415
00:21:27,266 --> 00:21:29,000
The one embarrassed will only be you.

416
00:21:30,288 --> 00:21:31,777
I don't want to talk to you.

417
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:33,500
I'll have your company deal with you.

418
00:21:34,088 --> 00:21:36,460
Your behavior hasn't been proper
for just a day or two,

419
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:38,620
and Li Weifeng isn't the only victim.

420
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:39,380
So,

421
00:21:40,288 --> 00:21:41,460
if you have anything to say,

422
00:21:41,644 --> 00:21:43,777
go explain it to your company's
Human Resources Department.

423
00:21:44,222 --> 00:21:45,900
Once I go to Human Resources tomorrow,

424
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:48,220
Li Weifeng might lose
his job before I do.

425
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:52,780
Will you buy me a coffee?

426
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:57,820
Thank you.

427
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:06,540
Miss Zhou,

428
00:22:07,860 --> 00:22:09,580
you can't rely on your looks forever.

429
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,020
So you think

430
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,740
it's either looks or brains?

431
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:16,580
As far as I know, your company's

432
00:22:16,580 --> 00:22:18,100
senior management is all men.

433
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:19,260
So what?

434
00:22:20,020 --> 00:22:21,860
Do all men behave like your husband,

435
00:22:21,860 --> 00:22:23,311
getting into office relationships?

436
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:25,060
You were the one seducing Li Weifeng.

437
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:26,580
He's a very honest man.

438
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:37,420
These are all my
chat records with Li Weifeng.

439
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:38,666
You can take a look.

440
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:42,580
From beginning to end,
he was the one who confessed to me.

441
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,140
I only replied when it was about work.

442
00:22:49,111 --> 00:22:50,660
He even tried to give me some gifts,

443
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,022
and I didn't accept them.

444
00:22:52,266 --> 00:22:53,622
You're still here, Ms. Zhou?

445
00:22:53,666 --> 00:22:54,260
Leaving now.

446
00:22:54,355 --> 00:22:54,980
See you tomorrow.

447
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:55,420
Okay.

448
00:22:58,020 --> 00:22:58,977
Going back, Ms. Zhou?

449
00:22:58,980 --> 00:22:59,420
Bye.

450
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,820
Including the necklace
you're wearing right now,

451
00:23:13,577 --> 00:23:15,260
he originally meant to give it to me.

452
00:23:19,020 --> 00:23:20,700
I don't know what Li Weifeng is like

453
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:21,420
in front of you.

454
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:22,900
You say he's honest,

455
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,700
but the Li Weifeng who talks to me

456
00:23:24,822 --> 00:23:26,555
(Long time since I slept with my wife.)
is not honest at all.

457
00:23:26,666 --> 00:23:28,200
(Your boyfriend doesn't pick you up.)
If I submit

458
00:23:28,222 --> 00:23:29,977
these messages
to the Human Resources Department,

459
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:31,980
he will be fired

460
00:23:32,422 --> 00:23:33,820
and sued for sexual harassment.

461
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:36,860
So you'd better
sincerely apologize to me now

462
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:38,900
and write to my company

463
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:40,410
to withdraw your accusations against me.

464
00:23:40,422 --> 00:23:41,844
Otherwise, I'll sue you as well.

465
00:23:46,940 --> 00:23:48,100
(Clear Chat History)

466
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:50,488
(Confirm deletion of chat history
with Li Weifeng? Clear)

467
00:23:57,340 --> 00:23:58,900
I've already deleted the chat records.

468
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:00,500
You have no evidence now.

469
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:08,620
What did you just ask me?

470
00:24:09,420 --> 00:24:10,940
Who the problem lies with, right?

471
00:24:11,288 --> 00:24:12,060
Of course it's you.

472
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:14,380
The way you look is the problem.

473
00:24:17,540 --> 00:24:18,580
I don't drink coffee.

474
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:20,380
This one

475
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:22,700
is for you.

476
00:24:36,644 --> 00:24:37,888
Just the two of us?

477
00:24:38,266 --> 00:24:39,288
Where's Lin Zhanqiao?

478
00:24:39,511 --> 00:24:40,844
If the three of us go together,

479
00:24:40,866 --> 00:24:41,900
it won't be lunch

480
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:43,580
but a shareholders' meeting.

481
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:47,140
You know I'm not really into food.

482
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,420
That's because

483
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:50,260
